g.text: That's really cool!... but won't this break if, after
a while, I change my models? 🖥️💔
Of course, which is why it has schema tracking.
g.g:
Í You use a model, it saves "version 1" of that model's schema. You update it, it goes "whoa!" and saves the updated model schema, with a new version, generates a migration file that you use to uplift all existing data, and halts the run.
✓
